    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1914-04-25T00:36:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1914-04-25T00:36:00-05:00" n="1076"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d1076">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.11/3801.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Consul <persName type="from">Canada</persName> to the <gloss
                            type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Consulate</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Vera Cruz</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1914-04-24T23:00:00-06:36">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 24, 1914, 11 p.m.</hi>
                        </date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Department’s April 24, 9 p.m. We have made every possible effort to get this
                    message through to Mexico City but it has been returned to us and we are
                    informed that all wires have been down since 9.30 this morning and that this
                    message cannot be sent; that it is impossible to tell when wires will be
                    repaired. Cable company states it has also informed Department. Since my April
                    24, 10 a.m. informed from most reliable source large number Americans in
                    addition those mentioned arrested vicinity Tierra Blanca and imprisoned at
                    Cordoba.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Canada</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
